net.cloud.server.file.request

Class SaveRequest<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.server.file.request.FileRequest<T>
      • net.cloud.server.file.request.SaveRequest<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the object used to represent the file
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileOutputStreamRequest, PrintWriterRequest, XmlSaveRequest

    public abstract class SaveRequest<T>
extends FileRequest<T>
    A FileRequest which in particular is requesting that a file be loaded and prepared for writing to. Some SaveRequests may also return a file object which can be read from, and in these situations nothing will prevent it. (Consider it a READ/WRITE mode)
